ages/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-059-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-059-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-059-1200w.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Промышленная обвязка с насосами\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"></picture></div><figcaption class=\"p-4\"><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-blue\">Промышленная обвязка с насосами</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Промышленная насосная группа</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400\">PHOTO_059</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm \"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-100\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-480w.webp 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-768w.webp 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-1200w.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\"><img src=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-1200w.jpg\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-063-1200w.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Нижний узел с насосом\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"></picture></div><figcaption class=\"p-4\"><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-blue\">Нижний узел с насосом</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Горизонтальный прибор, но вокруг промышленная обвязка</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400\">PHOTO_063</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm \"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-100\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-480w.webp 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-768w.webp 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-1200w.webp 941w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\"><img src=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-1200w.jpg\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-070-1200w.jpg 941w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" width=\"941\" height=\"1672\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Открытый блок управления и трубная обвязка\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"></picture></div><figcaption class=\"p-4\"><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-blue\">Открытый блок управления и трубная обвязка</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Комбинированная система; использовать только с нейтральной подписью</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400\">PHOTO_070</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm \"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-100\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-480w.webp 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-768w.webp 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-1200w.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\"><img src=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-1200w.jpg\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-080-1200w.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Коллекторная и фильтрационная группа\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"></picture></div><figcaption class=\"p-4\"><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-blue\">Коллекторная и фильтрационная группа</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Только как общий контекст; слишком широкая коллекторная система</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400\">PHOTO_080</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm \"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-100\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-480w.webp 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-768w.webp 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-1200w.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\"><img src=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-1200w.jpg\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-083-1200w.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Трубопроводная группа с измерительными приборами\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"></picture></div><figcaption class=\"p-4\"><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-blue\">Трубопроводная группа с измерительными приборами</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Измерительные приборы видны, но узел слишком общий</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400\">PHOTO_083</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm \"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-100\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-480w.webp 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-768w.webp 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-1200w.webp 941w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\"><img src=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-1200w.jpg\" srcset=\"assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-480w.jpg 480w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-768w.jpg 768w, assets/images/responsive/water-heaters-wh4/case-trehfaznaya-sistema-gvs-chastnogo-doma-photo-084-1200w.jpg 941w\" si